# Apivo

Cross-platform Flutter API client. See `AGENTS.md` for full architecture.

## Stack

Flutter + Riverpod + go_router + Dio + Drift. Dart SDK ^3.12.

## Structure

- `lib/features/<feature>/` — domain, data, presentation (feature-first)
- `lib/core/` — theme, router, network, logging, utils
- `lib/shared/` — reusable widgets and layout only
- `lib/database/tables/` — Drift schemas

## Non-negotiables

- No cross-feature imports; share via `core/` or `shared/`.
- User-facing strings → `AppStrings` in `core/constants/app_strings.dart`.
- Styling → design tokens (`AppSpacing`, `AppColors`, theme), not literals.
- State → Riverpod `Notifier` + immutable state with `copyWith`.
- Routes → `RoutePaths` / `RouteNames`; register in `app_router.dart`.

## Scope discipline

Match existing patterns. Minimal diffs. Reuse `AppButton`, `AppCard`, `AppTextField`, etc.
